{
  "stem": "1132.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And one of the-- I remember being picked up and taken down to the basement.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This is memory.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Middle of the night, middle of the day, regardless of-- of what time, whenever this came and the sirens sounded, you ran to the basement.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Now, one of the most striking memories-- and again, this is memory-- that the bomb fell somewhere around us.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I mean, imagine when you get bombed out.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we were extremely lucky that it wasn't our building, but the building directly across the street from us.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Imagine when the air raid is over and you are allowed to come out from the basement, and you look across the street and you see a house totally open.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I mean, I think it was a five, six story high apartment house, and everything is hanging.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It-- it-- this is a memory, again, that I will never, ever forget.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So I think the fact that Hungary was the last country that the Germans occupied, and Hungary was among the last to have all of the effects of the war, are significant to the story, and that I survived all of that in that city.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Going back to, now, this other apartment house near the Danube where we ended up moving to, raids were becoming extremely common there.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We heard the street fights.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "At this point, the Germans were really getting into trouble because the Russians were really pushing them.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "This is all within about eight to 10 months that all this has happened.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I remember-- and again, this is a distinct memory of mine-- I remember clearly having air raids and having the Nazis and the Arrowheads coming in.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And at one point at one of the air raids, we were, again, down in the basement.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
